ce to half?","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Waveband convergence rate at 67%, 70%... 75%... Steadily increasing. It's working!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Shhh, shush...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"Be quiet. It's a crucial moment!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"\"You\"... Hmm. \"You and I\"... Sing... \"Song\"?","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"...Sky... What's that supposed to mean? And what is the last word? Love... Sorrow?","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"No, hold it, I need to hear it one more time... I didn't catch all of it...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"...Too late. The signal's already gone...","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"What? Oh, excuse me! I've been trying to understand this <color=Highlight>\"phantom\"</color>, and I got overexcited for a moment... And yes, please talk anytime you want!","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002},{"text":"I'm Jiuyue, a researcher studying the fog in Whining Aix's Mire, from the Academy. I've been researching TD Ecoacoustics in this area.","quest_name":"Stygian Lacrimosa","quest_id":118000002}]}